<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:12.0pt">Guys,<br>
<br>
Don't do it.&nbsp; It doesn't work at all.&nbsp; I couldn't pick up maintenance of it either, and the majority of the Windows support is removed as Ralph said.&nbsp; Just use MPICH for Windows work and save yourself the pain.<br>
<br>
Cheers,<br>
<br>
Damien<o:p></o:p></p>
